# Workflow Preferences

- Focus only on the areas of code relevant to the current task
- Do not touch code unrelated to the task at hand
- Write thorough tests for all major functionality
- Avoid making major architectural changes to a feature that is already working well, unless explicitly instructed to do so
- Always consider what other methods and areas of the codebase may be affected by any code change before making it
